annotations.caption: In a factory building, a man whistles and walks with an iron bar, and a man comes up in the distance with a flashlight.

A woman wearing a hat and a black dress skateboard outside, the woman jumped on the skateboard and fell to the ground. The picture turns, the woman successfully stands on the skateboard after jumping on the skateboard, the woman makes a whiny sound.
The fingers are pressed constantly on the piano keyboard, and the piano makes a corresponding melodious sound.
A color background picture with amplitudes and notes slowly disappears into a black, whistling sound.
A large white wind indicator whirled in the wind, rustling leaves around it.
